# Copy to terraform.tfvars and adjust if needed.
#   cp terraform.tfvars.example terraform.tfvars
#
# In Cloud Shell you can usually leave `project` blank - Terraform picks up the
# active project from GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT.

